        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98">
                Mr. Garro Jones
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-10-16/debates/a889ccf9-2c51-4aed-8c61-aa06574b4e44/SelectCommitteeOnNationalExpenditure#contribution-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I ask my right hon. Friend whether, having regard to his statement that the Select Committee were not informed of the operational aspects of their report, he contemplates making any provision in future that these <span id="1503" class="column-number" data-column-number="1503"></span> Committees can be informed of the operational aspect of their reports to prevent a recurrence of the serious difference which has arisen in this case?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-10-16/debates/a889ccf9-2c51-4aed-8c61-aa06574b4e44/SelectCommitteeOnNationalExpenditure#contribution-c6f75ef5-2567-4023-8a1f-a6be217cff98">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
